  "title": "WSH Coordinator (MRT Construction Project)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure compliance of operations with Workplace Safety and Health/Environmental Control regulations and statutory requirements</li>\n  <li>Implements, monitor and maintain appropriate safety measurements in accordance with the Workplace Health and Safety Act</li>\n  <li>Enforces all safety requirements and in-house safety rules and regulations</li>\n  <li>Conducts regular site checks and takes appropriate corrective actions</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess Level \"B\" Certificate and other related courses</li>\n  <li>LTA (MRT/Tunnel/Road) Project Experience required, comfortable to work on 6-days 12-hour schedule workweek</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working experience in tunneling from construction industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p>\n<p>Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367</p>\n<p>bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
